\c 23
\p
\v 15 Vanakomana vaMosesi: Gerishomi naEriezeri.
\v 16 Vanakomana vaGerishomi: Shebhueri mukuru.
\v 17 Vanakomana vaEriezeri: Rehabhia mukuru. Eriezeri akanga asina vamwe vanakomana; asi vanakomana vaRehabhia vakanga vari vazhinji-zhinji.
\v 18 Vanakomana valshari: Sheromiti mukuru.
\p
\v 19 Vanakomana vaHebhuroni: Jeria mukuru, Amaria wechipiri, Jahazieri wechitatu, Jekameami wechina.
\v 20 Vanakomana vaUzieri: Mika mukuru, naIshia wechipiri.
\p
\v 21 Vanakomana vaMerari: Mari naMushi. Vanakomana vaMari: Eriazari naKishi.
\v 22 Eriazari akafa asina vanakomana, asi vanasikana voga; hama dzavo, vanakomana vaKishi, dzikavawana.
\v 23 Vanakomana vaMushi: Mari, naEdheri, naJeremoti, vose vatatu.
\p
\v 24 Ndivo vaiva vanakomana vaRevhi, nedzimba dzamadzibaba avo, ivo vakuru vedzimba dzamadzibaba vakaverengwa pakati pavo, vachiverengwa namazita avo musoro womumwe nomumwe, vaibata basa paimba yaJehovha, vanamakore makumi maviri navakapfuura ipapo.
\p
\v 25 Nokuti Dhavhidhi wakati, "Jehovha Mwari waIsiraeri wakazorodza vanhu vake; iye anogara Jerusaremu nokusingaperi,
\v 26 uye vaRevhi havachazofaniri kutakura tabhenekari nenhumbi dzayo dzokubata mabasa ayo."
\v 27 Nokuti namashoko aDhavhidhi okupedzisira vanakomana vaRevhi vakaverengwa, vanamakore makumi maviri navakapfuura ipapo.
\v 28 Nokuti basa ravo rakanga riri rokubatsira vanakomana vaAroni pakushumira paimba yaJehovha, pavazhe, napamakamuri, napakusuka zvinhu zvitsvene, riri basa rokushumira paimba yaMwari;
\v 29 nokugadzira zvingwa zvokuratidza, noupfu hwakatsetseka hwechipiriso choupfu, kana chezvingwa zvitete zvisina mbiriso, kana zvakabikwa mugango, kana zvakakanyiwa namafuta, marudzi ose ezviyero nezvitanda zvokuera
\v 30 nazvo, nokum‘ra mangwanan ose vachivonga nokurumbidza Jehovha, uye madekwanawo saizvozvo;
\v 31 nokubayira Jehovha zvipiriso zvose zvinopiswa, pamaSabata, napakugara kwemwedzi, napamitambo yakatarwa panguva dzose dza‑
\p karairwa, mazuva ose pamberi paJehovha.
\v 32 Uye kuti vachengete tende rokusangana, nokuchengeta nzvimbo tsvene, nokuchengeta vanakomana vaAroni, hama dzavo, pabasa reimba yaJehovha.
